data.title: Today’s famous birthdays list for March 5, 2023 includes celebrities Niki Taylor, Eva Mendes
data.meta_description: Celebrities Niki Taylor and Eva Mendes share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of famous people with birthdays on March 5, 2023 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Niki Taylor, Eva Mendes and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on March 5th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on March 5, 2023

Magician Penn Jillette turns 68

Fun fact: Awarded a Star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame in 2013

Actor Paul Blackthorne turns 54

Fun fact: Once portrayed the lead character from ‘The Dresden Files’ series of novels on SyFy

Actress Eva Mendes turns 49

Fun fact: One of her early acting appearances was in an episode of ‘ER’ where she played a babysitter

Actor and director Kevin Connolly turns 49

Fun fact: First feature film he appeared in was ‘Rocky V’ in 1990

Model Niki Taylor turns 48

Fun fact: Her middle name is Renee

More celebrities with birthdays today

Actor Paul Sand (“St. Elsewhere”) is 91. Actor James B. Sikking (“Hill Street Blues,” ″Doogie Howser, M.D.”) is 89. Football player-turned-actor Fred Williamson is 85. Actor Samantha Eggar (“The Molly Maguires,” ″Dr. Doolittle”) is 84. Actor Michael Warren (“Soul Food,” ″Hill Street Blues”) is 77. Actor Eddie Hodges is 76. Singer Eddy Grant is 75. Keyboardist Alan Clark of Dire Straits is 71. Actor-comedian Marsha Warfield (“Night Court”) is 69. Actor Adriana Barraza is 67. Actor Talia Balsam (“Divorce,” ″Mad Men”) is 64. Musicians Charlie and Craig Reid of The Proclaimers are 61. Guitarist John Frusciante (Red Hot Chili Peppers) is 53. Singer Rome is 53. Actor Jolene Blalock (“Star Trek: Enterprise”) is 48. Actor Kimberly McCullough (“General Hospital”) is 45. Actor Karolina Wydra (“Wicked City,” “House”) is 42. Musician Amanda Shires (The Highwomen, Jason Isbell and the 400 Unit) is 41. Actor Sterling Knight (“Sonny With A Chance”) is 34. Actor Jake Lloyd (“Star Wars” films) is 34. Actor Micah Fowler (“Speechless”) is 25.
